Company Overview of Investure, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Investure, LLC is an employee owned asset management firm. The firm provides its services to high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, endowment, and foundations. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios and alternative assets. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative markets across the globe. It also invests in emerging markets. The firm primarily invests in stocks, bonds, hedge funds, and private equity. Investure, LLC was founded in 2003 and is based in Charlottesville, Virginia.


126 Garrett St, Suite JCharlottesville, VA 22902United StatesFounded in 2003



