Investure











 











About Us


Our Guiding Principles


Team


Clients





Investure, LLC is a recognized leader in the endowment and foundation investment management 
                industry having pioneered the full-service outsourced investment office model. We are focused 
                on the investment management needs of non-profits serving as the investment office for a 
                select group of prestigious colleges and foundations. 
                Investure currently manages approximately $13 billion* across all asset classes. We seek 
                to build long-term relationships with our clients by bringing the distinct capabilities 
                and advantages of a larger investment office to mid-sized endowments and foundations.
                
                * as of March 2017   
                




                Copyright &copy 2017 by Investure, LLC Terms of Use





